    <title>Install the Linus system on Windows</title>
    <url>/2021/Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Install-the-Linus-system-on-Windows"><a href="#Install-the-Linus-system-on-Windows" class="headerlink" title="Install the Linus system on Windows"></a>Install the Linus system on Windows</h1><p>Author: Hsuan-Ting Lai</p>
<hr>
<hr>
<h1 id="中文版"><a href="#中文版" class="headerlink" title="中文版"></a>中文版</h1><h2 id="Step-1-啟用Windows-Linus-System"><a href="#Step-1-啟用Windows-Linus-System" class="headerlink" title="Step 1 啟用Windows Linus System"></a>Step 1 啟用Windows Linus System</h2><p>需要先啟用 Windows Linux Subsystem 功能。需在『開啟或關閉 Windows 功能中設定』，剛裝完畢後，需要重新開機。</p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%201.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<h2 id="Step-2-安裝Ubuntu"><a href="#Step-2-安裝Ubuntu" class="headerlink" title="Step 2 安裝Ubuntu"></a>Step 2 安裝Ubuntu</h2><p>接著到Windows Store 裡就有 Ubuntu App 可以選擇安裝</p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%202.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<p>安裝成功後，就可以在 Windows 選單找到 Ubuntu App</p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%203.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>啟動Ubuntu後卻發現出現錯誤訊息…..</strong>  <img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%204.png" alt="Untitled">  這表示Windows-Subsystem-Linux (WSL)還沒打開，因此可以用接下來的方法解決。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="Step-3-開啟PowerShell"><a href="#Step-3-開啟PowerShell" class="headerlink" title="Step 3 開啟PowerShell"></a>Step 3 開啟PowerShell</h2><p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%205.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<p><strong>輸入以下指令:</strong></p>
<p><code>Enable-WindowsOptionalFeature -Online -FeatureName Microsoft-Windows-Subsystem-Linux</code></p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%206.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<h2 id="Step-4-啟動Ubuntu"><a href="#Step-4-啟動Ubuntu" class="headerlink" title="Step 4 啟動Ubuntu"></a>Step 4 啟動Ubuntu</h2><p><strong>安裝成功！</strong></p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%207.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<p>原本的 C/D/F 槽都 mount 在 /mnt 下</p>
<p>輸入<code>cd /mnt/c/Users/*Name/Desktop</code> </p>
<p>*Name: 根據自己的電腦名稱去修改</p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%208.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<h2 id="Step-5-更新套件"><a href="#Step-5-更新套件" class="headerlink" title="Step 5 更新套件"></a>Step 5 更新套件</h2><p>輸入 <code>sudo apt-get update</code></p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%209.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<p><strong>Done!</strong></p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%2010.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<h1 id="English-version"><a href="#English-version" class="headerlink" title="English version"></a>English version</h1><h2 id="Step-1-Turn-on-Windows-Linux-Subsystem"><a href="#Step-1-Turn-on-Windows-Linux-Subsystem" class="headerlink" title="Step 1. Turn on Windows Linux Subsystem"></a>Step 1. Turn on Windows Linux Subsystem</h2><ol>
<li>Press <strong>“Windows”</strong> + “<strong>R</strong>” keys simultaneously to open the Run prompt.</li>
<li>Type in “<strong>Control</strong> <strong>Panel</strong>”</li>
<li>Click on the “<strong>Programs</strong> <strong>and</strong> <strong>Features</strong>” option.</li>
<li>Select the “<strong>Turn Windows Features On or OFF</strong>” option in the left pane.</li>
<li>Scroll down and select “<strong>Windows Subsystem for Linux</strong>“</li>
<li>6.<strong>Click</strong> on “<strong>OK</strong>” to enable the feature.</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%2011.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%2012.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<h2 id="Step-2-Install-Ubuntu"><a href="#Step-2-Install-Ubuntu" class="headerlink" title="Step 2 Install Ubuntu"></a>Step 2 Install Ubuntu</h2><ol>
<li>Open the <strong>Microsoft Store</strong> from the Start menu, and search for “<strong>Ubuntu</strong>” in the store</li>
<li>To install , click it, and then click the “Get” or “Install” button to install it like any other Store application.</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%2013.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<h2 id="Step-3-Turning-WSL-ON-Through-PowerShell"><a href="#Step-3-Turning-WSL-ON-Through-PowerShell" class="headerlink" title="Step 3 Turning WSL ON Through PowerShell"></a>Step 3 Turning WSL ON Through PowerShell</h2><ol>
<li>Search for PowerShell, right-click the top result, and select the <strong>Run as administrator option.</strong></li>
<li>Type the following command to enable the Linux subsystem and press Enter: <code>Enable-WindowsOptionalFeature -Online -FeatureName Microsoft-Windows-Subsystem-Linux</code> Type <strong>Y</strong> and press <strong>Enter t</strong>o confirm and restart your computer. <img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%2014.png" alt="Untitled"></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="Step-4-Open-Ubuntu"><a href="#Step-4-Open-Ubuntu" class="headerlink" title="Step 4 Open Ubuntu"></a>Step 4 Open Ubuntu</h2><ol>
<li>Open Start, and click it . <img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%2015.png" alt="Untitled"></li>
</ol>
<p>I<strong>t works!</strong></p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%2016.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<h2 id="Step-5-Update"><a href="#Step-5-Update" class="headerlink" title="Step 5 Update"></a>Step 5 Update</h2><p>This is the first time you are using your system after installing, you should run the update command: <code>sudo apt-get update</code></p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%209.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<p><strong>Done!</strong></p>
<p><img src="Install%20the%20Linus%20system%20on%20Windows/Untitled%2010.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<h1 id="References"><a href="#References" class="headerlink" title="References"></a>References</h1><p><a href="https://medium.com/@misscoming/%E5%9C%A8-windows-10-%E4%B8%8A%E8%B7%91-ubuntu-18-04-92f80b2d725b">在 Windows 10 上跑 Ubuntu 18.04</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.howtogeek.com/249966/how-to-install-and-use-the-linux-bash-shell-on-windows-10/">How to Install and Use the Linux Bash Shell on Windows 10</a></p>
<p><a href="https://appuals.com/how-to-fix-the-wsl-optional-component-is-not-enabled-please-enable-it-and-try-again-error-on-ubuntu/">How to Fix ‘The WSL Optional Component is not Enabled. Please Enable it and Try again’ Error on Ubuntu? - Appuals.com</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.windowscentral.com/install-windows-subsystem-linux-windows-10">Do you want to run Linux on Windows 10? Use WSL, here’s how.</a></p>
]]></content>
